metadata.name: Fairy love
metadata.description:
Once there was a young girl and she had many dreams. She also lost her lover many years ago, but by chance one day she went to the fairy city and became a beautiful fairy. Now she has another goal. She wants to fulfill the wishes of others so that everyone can find their love because there is nothing more beautiful than love, so that no one is in pain and suffering.
This is the fairy town and she is looking for true love.
